#Descriptions
info.colorfulmobs.colorwand=When right clicked while looking at a mob, the color GUI will be displayed. The color GUI allows the player to change RGB and transparency.
info.colorfulmobs.ghostdust=When used on a mob, it will become 20% more transparent. This can also be applied using dispensers. 
info.colorfulmobs.powder=Dye powder can be applied to almost any mob. Doing so will change that mobs color to be like the color of the dye. This can also be applied using a dispenser.
info.colorfulmobs.rainbowdust=When used on a mob, the mob will be changed to a random color. This can also be applied using dispensers.
info.colorfulmobs.datachecker=When used on a mob, relevent information will be posted to the chat. This includes the RGB, transparency and mob name.
info.colorfulmobs.radiantdust=When used on a mob, it will gain the radiant effect. This effect will cause the mob to slowly change between colors. This will cause all other color and transparency settings to be ignored. 